        (a / alpha
           :ARG0 b
           :ARG1 (g / gamma
                    :ARG0-of (b / beta)))"""

assert reconfigure(g) == Tree(('a', [('/', 'alpha'), (':ARG0', ('b', [('/',
    'beta')])), (':ARG1', ('g', [('/', 'gamma'), (':ARG0-of', 'b')]))]))
assert reconfigure(g, key=model.canonical_order) == Tree(('a', [('/',
    'alpha'), (':ARG0', ('b', [('/', 'beta'), (':ARG0', ('g', [('/',
    'gamma')]))])), (':ARG1', 'g')]))
